name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
Many netizens asked me to pay attention to the increase in electricity prices in Shanghai in December. I searched and found that not only Shanghai, but many places said that they had increased prices.
But many people on Zhihu also listed data and formulas to say that there was no price increase. I don’t understand these, so it’s hard to make a judgment.
So I thought I might as well ask everyone, did your electricity bill increase in December?
